data.description: Great yard to be found in this well kept Mintbrook home on a corner lot. Detached side entry two car garage is a big plus especially vs. alley access. House is so comfortable and versitle...it is laid out well for cozy, private evenings or entertaining the whole gang. Working from home is easy. Great breakfast area, formal dining room as well as a wonderfully blended kitchen/living room area that accommodates quiet living or that monster TV you've always wanted. Speakers are integrated throughout the house for whole home listening. New Lennox HVAC and Next Pro installed in July 2023!
